{"id":381815,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":13}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"130","ytitle":"","mtitle":"扫盲所见","ftitle":"","authors":["胡文伯"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡文伯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕鸡叫一百回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“娃他妈，快睡去!明天还要下地哩!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“早着哩，我这课生字还不会。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“早啥哩!鸡已叫过四五回。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“管它哩，这课不学会，哪怕鸡叫一百回。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你从头考到尾"}]}